  <summary date="2021-04-13T22:25:34Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Forced Arbitration Injustice Repeal Act

This bill prohibits a predispute arbitration agreement from being valid or enforceable if it requires arbitration of an employment, consumer, antitrust, or civil rights dispute.</summary>
